name: Poo Doge
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: PooDoge is a portfolio tracking and charting suite on Dogechain that provides investors with the tools to trade smarter while keeping track of all their token investments whether they are listed on big exchanges or not.
